	<Title>
		Hodgkin&apos;s vs. non-Hodgkin&apos;s lymphoma
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		The difference between Hodgkin&apos;s and non-Hodgkin&apos;s lymphoma is the type of cell involved.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		What&apos;s the difference between Hodgkin&apos;s disease and non-Hodgkin&apos;s lymphoma?
